{
  "id": "61e91b3bb3495c001e9ef971",
  "title": "(4.3.2.3) Measure and control speed",
  "created": 1551942905,
  "updated": 1556600738,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1cd",
      "text": "(4.3.2.3) Measure and control speed",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1553661586,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1ce",
      "text": "As a major difference from the Whole Mind System, the [Focus Reading]  emphasis measurement. After reading a book, you should record the followings: ",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1556600738,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1cf",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1d0",
      "text": "\tthe number of pages of the book you read",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1d1",
      "text": "\tthe time spent to read the book",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1d2",
      "text": "\thow much you feel you understand the book.",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1556600699,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1d3",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1d4",
      "text": "By keeping track of those measurement result, you understand your current abilities. You need to understand your ability to control the speed according to the level of understanding you want. For those whose understanding is [bottleneck], it is important to read in optimum speed, not to read faster. ",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1d5",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1d6",
      "text": "If you read too fast, you do not reach the level of understanding you want. If you read too late, your level of understanding is high, but the range that you can read in unit time go narrower. By controlling to the optimum speed, you get the best performance without stress.",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1d7",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1d8",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/e67dbb74e5ff52e3c2c65f3d0f95d7c5]",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1d9",
      "text": "Fig: [The relationship between reading speed, range and quantity of knowledge]",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942943,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1da",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1553592976,
      "updated": 1553592976,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1db",
      "text": "\t[読む速度] = [reading speed]",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1553593013,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1dc",
      "text": "\t\tup: [遅い] = [slow]",
      "created": 1553593013,
      "updated": 1553593020,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1dd",
      "text": "\t\tdown: [速い] = [fast]",
      "created": 1553593020,
      "updated": 1553593032,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1de",
      "text": "\tThree sentences in the middle",
      "created": 1553593039,
      "updated": 1553593046,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1df",
      "text": "\t\tThe level of understanding is high, but it is too slow to read the whole.",
      "created": 1551943114,
      "updated": 1553593046,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1e0",
      "text": " \tYou read whole content with the level of understanding you want in the same time.",
      "created": 1551943419,
      "updated": 1553593046,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1e1",
      "text": " \tYou read it in a shorter time, but you do not reach the level of understanding you want.",
      "created": 1551943419,
      "updated": 1553593048,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1e2",
      "text": " [得られた知識の量] = [the quantity of information you got]",
      "created": 1551943419,
      "updated": 1553593063,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1e3",
      "text": "\t\t[多い] = large, large, [少ない] = small",
      "created": 1551943095,
      "updated": 1553593082,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1e4",
      "text": "\t[読んだ範囲] = the range you read",
      "created": 1551943508,
      "updated": 1553593093,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1e5",
      "text": "\t\t[狭い] = nallow, [広い] = wide, wide",
      "created": 1551943526,
      "updated": 1553593110,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1e6",
      "text": "\t[最適な速度] = [optimum speed]",
      "created": 1551943532,
      "updated": 1553593122,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1e7",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551943095,
      "updated": 1551943095,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1e8",
      "text": "If you read too fast and you did not understand enough, you can read it again. However, if you read too slow, you waste your time, and you can not regain it. So, if you do not understand the optimum balance, you should better to read fast. That goes similar to the repetitive reading of the Whole Mind System.",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1e9",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942950,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1ea",
      "text": "On the other hand, when you read about unfamiliar content, sometimes you can not grasp the content at all. It is a sign that the speed is too fast.",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1eb",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1551942905,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1ec",
      "text": "Because it is inexperienced content, you have to read slowly rather than usual, but you read at an ordinary speed, and your speed of understanding can not catch up with. In such a case, [reading aloud] may have good effects. It slows your reading speed. The learning technique \"Shakyo\" introduced in [(1.3.4.1) Shakyo] is also a way to slow your reading speed. I explain other ways to read difficult books slowly from the section [(4.4) Reading one page in three minutes to assemble information].",
      "created": 1551942905,
      "updated": 1553660380,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1ed",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1553593142,
      "updated": 1553593142,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3baff09e0000d0b1ee",
      "text": "[en.icon]",
      "created": 1556600738,
      "updated": 1556600738,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    }
  ]
}